OL,3,CAnimals convey King's wishes to Sir
OL,4,CDavid Attenborough on 100th birthday
OL,6,FThe animal kingdom came together to
OL,7,Ftransport a birthday card from King
OL,8,FCharles to Sir David Attenborough, who
OL,9,Fcelebrated his 100th birthday on
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,12,FIn a video screened as part of
OL,13,Fcelebrations at the Royal Albert Hall,
OL,14,Fa chain of animals transported the
OL,15,Fnote from Balmoral Castle to Sir
OL,16,FDavid's London home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
