PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778385837
OL,3,CAnimals convey King's wishes to Sir
OL,4,CDavid Attenborough on 100th birthday
OL,6,FHe was described as "a remarkable man"
OL,7,Fand a "marvellous presenter" before
OL,8,Fthe concert, which featured musical
OL,9,Fperformances and montages of some of
OL,10,FSir David's most memorable work.
OL,12,FThe creature courier service started
OL,13,Fwith a border collie sheepdog called
OL,14,FFlynn and features eagles, a hedgehog,
OL,15,Fa red squirrel, a flock of geese, an
OL,16,Fotter, a swan, a duck, a fox, a deer,
OL,17,Fand finally barn owl Lily, who posts
OL,18,Fthe letter through Sir David's
OL,19,Fletterbox.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778385837
OL,3,CAnimals convey King's wishes to Sir
OL,4,CDavid Attenborough on 100th birthday
OL,6,FThe King recounted a seven-decade
OL,7,Ffriendship with the naturalist, with
OL,8,Fthe pair having first met when the
OL,9,Fthen nine-year-old Prince Charles
OL,10,Fvisited the set of the BBC children's
OL,11,Fprogramme Zoo Quest in 1958 with his
OL,12,Fsister Princess Anne.
OL,14,FKing Charles enlists friends from the
OL,15,Fanimal kingdom to congratulate David
OL,16,FAttenborough on his 100th birthday
OL,18,FThe Queen's adopted dog Moley also
OL,19,Fmade a cameo in the film.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778385837
OL,3,CAnimals convey King's wishes to Sir
OL,4,CDavid Attenborough on 100th birthday
OL,6,FThe King was "delighted" to feature in
OL,7,Fthe tribute, according to Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace, and followed each stage of the
OL,9,Ffilming process "with great interest".
OL,11,F"He was only sorry not to meet Lily
OL,12,Fthe magical barn owl in person," the
OL,13,Fstatement said.
OL,15,F"Her Majesty was particularly touched
OL,16,Fthat her mischievous Moley was invited
OL,17,Fto make a cameo appearance and was on
OL,18,Fhand with a ready selection of dog
OL,19,Ftreats to help coax a willing
OL,20,Fperformance on the day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
