PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1778385837
OL,3,CAnimals convey King's wishes to Sir
OL,4,CDavid Attenborough on 100th birthday
OL,6,F"The King and Queen send their warmest
OL,7,Fwishes to Sir David on his special
OL,8,Fnight and hope he enjoys the resulting
OL,9,Ffilm as much as they enjoyed making
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
